{"word":"λυπέω","slug":"λυπέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>λυπέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:λύπη\">λύπη</a></el>] ‘be engaged in grief’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> <b>cause grief/sorrow <a href='B:540 2:2'>2 Cor 2:2</a>, <a href='B:540 2:5'>5</a>; <a href='B:540 7:8'>7:8</a>; <a href='B:560 4:30'>Eph 4:30</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b>experience distress <a href='B:470 14:9'>Mt 14:9</a>; <a href='B:470 18:31'>18:31</a>; <a href='B:480 10:22'>Mk 10:22</a>; <a href='B:480 14:19'>14:19</a>; <a href='B:500 16:20'>J 16:20</a>; <a href='B:500 21:17'>21:17</a>; <a href='B:520 14:15'>Ro 14:15</a>; <a href='B:540 2:4'>2 Cor 2:4</a>; <a href='B:670 1:6'>1 Pt 1:6</a>.</b> W. focus on inward aspect <b>to sorrow, be distressed, be in grief <a href='B:470 19:22'>Mt 19:22</a>; <a href='B:470 26:22'>26:22</a>, <a href='B:470 26:37'>37</a>; <a href='B:480 10:22'>Mk 10:22</a>; <a href='B:540 6:10'>2 Cor 6:10</a>; <a href='B:590 4:13'>1 Th 4:13</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:λυμαίνομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:λύπη\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}